**LinkedIn Learning**
LinkedIn Learning is an online education platform with thousands of expert‑led video courses in business, technology, and creative subjects designed to help professionals learn new skills and upskill in their careers.
It personalizes learning paths based on your goals and offers quizzes, exercise files, and certificates you can add to your LinkedIn profile after completion.
The content ranges from beginner overviews to deeper skill refreshers across topics like cloud, data analysis, leadership, and software development.

Link: https://www.linkedin.com/learning/

