**LipDub AI**
LipDub AI is an AI‑powered tool that generates realistic lip‑synced video content, letting you translate, edit, or personalize dialogue in videos without reshooting. The platform uses proprietary AI to match lip movement to new audio tracks and supports professional‑grade features like voice cloning, multilingual dubbing, and high‑fidelity output for marketing, courses, and creative workflows. It’s aimed at helping teams scale video production and localization efficiently using AI lip‑sync technology.

Link: https://www.lipdub.ai/

